item.title: Prayer bpn12421 in Namibia
item.description: Hompa! Ronga vanuke vano. Vanuke vano mbo vimenwa vyamushikunino, dimucuko Doye, dimucuko damushipata Shoye. Renka mvhura yirokere pavo; renka liyuva lyaushiti litwedere pavo momu ghuna vishanene. Renka munku Ghoye ghuva fudire impo vawane lideuro, kukura nakurunduruka, nalimoneko lyaufughuli. Ove Mutapi. Ove Mufenkenda. (Source category: Rugciriku : LIKUSHONGO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12421)
